IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. DEBUG-STRUCT-TEST.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
CONFIGURATION SECTION.
OBJECT-COMPUTER. VULKAN-COMPUTE-SHADER.
SPECIAL-NAMES.
    LOCAL-SIZE IS (1, 1, 1).
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT BLOCK-DATA ASSIGN TO "GPU-BUFFER-0-0"
        ORGANIZATION IS ACCESS-STORAGE.
    SELECT SETTINGS ASSIGN TO "GPU-BUFFER-0-1"
        ORGANIZATION IS ACCESS-UNIFORM.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD BLOCK-DATA LAYOUT IS STD430.
01 FIELD-A PIC FLOAT.
01 FIELD-B PIC I.
FD SETTINGS LAYOUT IS STD140.
01 UNIFORM-DATA.
    05 SCALAR-F PIC FLOAT.
    05 SCALAR-I PIC I.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MAIN-LOGIC.
        MOVE 1.5 TO FIELD-A.
        MOVE 42 TO FIELD-B.
        MOVE SCALAR-F OF UNIFORM-DATA TO FIELD-A.
        MOVE SCALAR-I OF UNIFORM-DATA TO FIELD-B.
        GOBACK.
